Over 1,000 bags of poisonous foreign rice were seized by the Nigeria Customs Service on Thursday in Ogun



Acting Comptroller, FoU, Zone A, Hussein Ejibunu, during a press conference said that the bags of parboiled rice came into Cotonou from India.



The bags of rice were smuggled into the country through Benin Republic

